Chongqing Three Gorges Shares Rise 3.2% After Water Investment Report

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-05-24T01:31:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-24/chongqing-three-gorges-shares-rise-3-2-after-water-investment-report.html
Chongqing Three Gorges Water
Conservancy and Electric Power Co. shares opened 3.2 percent
higher at 18.49 yuan after Xinhua News Agency cited Minister of
Water Resources Chen Lei as saying China will increase
investment in water conservation projects this decade to 4
trillion yuan, up from  1.06 trillion yuan in the previous 10
years.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  